@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_drmjbt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.74 - v0 + 0.23)) * 0.14)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.97)) - wp.exp((v1 + 0.62 * v1 + 0.04)))
    v0 = (0.55 + (0.64 / (tmp + 0.67 / v2 + 0.88)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.99) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.96)) * 0.55)
    v1 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
